# Lab Progress

Completed Tasks:

• Installed Oracle VirtualBox
• Created Windows Server 2022 virtual machine
• Installed Windows Server 2022 Standard Evaluation
• Installed Active Directory Domain Services (AD DS)
• Promoted the server to a Domain Controller
• Created the domain: corp.local
• Opened Active Directory Users and Computers
• Created the first domain user account: Sarah Jones (sjones)

---

# IAM Task Example: User Provisioning

Example onboarding task:

New Employee: Sarah Jones
Department: Finance

Steps performed:

1. Open Active Directory Users and Computers
2. Navigate to Users container
3. Right-click → New → User
4. Enter employee information
5. Assign username (sjones)
6. Set temporary password
7. Require password change at first login

This simulates the onboarding process performed by IAM or IT helpdesk teams.


---

# Security Monitoring (Future Lab Work)

Later stages of this lab will include reviewing authentication logs using Windows Event Viewer.

Important security events include:

4624 – Successful login
4625 – Failed login attempt
4720 – User account created
4726 – User account deleted
4732 – User added to group

Monitoring these logs helps security teams detect suspicious authentication activity.

